MICROWAVE butter in 4-quart bowl on HIGH for 45 seconds. ADD marshmallows; mix to coat. Microwave 1-1/2 minutes or until melted, stirring after 45 seconds. Add cereal; mix to coat well. SHAPE 1 cup of the mixture into ball, using wet or greased hands. Repeat to make 6 large balls. Shape remaining mixture into 6 small balls (1/2 cup cereal mixture for each). CREATE 'Snow Person' by placing a small ball on top of each large ball. Press balls together. Use decorating icing to secure. DECORATE snow people using icing as glue for decorations.